Package: FPGC
Title: Help functions to process Phenotypic Genomic and Climate data
Version: 0.0.11
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Leo",
           family = "Crespo",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "leonardoabdiel@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: FPGC has three sets of functions 1) to process models from the lme4 package to obtain various trial statistics; 
                2)to format and filter genotypic data to generate G matrix; 
                and 3) to download and process climate data from the NASA POWER database.
